1	The above consolidated unaudited financial results have been prepared in accordance with Indian Accounting Standards as prescribed under section 133 of the Companies Act, 2013 read with Rule 3 of the Companies (Indian Accounting Standards) Rules, 2015 as amended from time to time.						 &lt;BR&gt; 
2	The above consolidated unaudited financial results were reviewed by the Audit Committee and subsequently approved by the Board of Directors at their meeting held on February 12, 2026 in in terms of Regulation 33 of SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulation 2015. The Statutory Auditors have expressed an unqualified opinion.						 &lt;BR&gt; 
